16 KURD GUERRILLAS KILLED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Turkish security forces killed 16 Kurdish guerrillas in the eastern province 
of Tunceli, where the army has launched a big offensive, the Anatolian News 
Agency said Sunday. 
