 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Steve Keith: 125-67 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS 
YR. HGT. P Blair Eldridge Sr. 6-2 F 04,16,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. P 
James Balagot Sr. 6-0 G Luke Carlson Sr. 6-6 C Darrell Parker Sr. 6-0 G 
04,15,05,06,04 TOP NEWCOMERS YR. HGT. P Shaun Guinn Jr. 5-11 G Jermaine Hill 
