</P>
<P>
 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Jerry DeBusk: 48-12 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS 
YR. HGT. P Dennis Keane Jr. 6-3 G Brendan Mulligan Sr. 6-3 G/F 04,16,05,06,05 
TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. P Jay Kramb Sr. 6-4 F Allen Krist Jr. 6-8 C Nick 
Maroutsos Sr. 6-4 F/G J.C. Timmons Sr. 6-2 G 04,16,05,06,05 TOP NEWCOMERS YR. 
