<P>
 Ford in Talks With Mazda: Ford Motor Co. said that talks with Mazda Motor 
Corp. are in "an advanced stage" for the production by Ford of a car for Mazda 
based on an existing Ford model. A U.S.-based Ford spokesman said he agreed 
with the general outlines of a report appearing in London's Sunday Times, but 
